          "text": "M2 EVT: confirm dominant proximal M2 division. EVT is reasonable for dominant proximal M2 (COR 2a, Section 4.7.2 Rec 7). EVT is not recommended for nondominant or codominant M2 (COR 3: No Benefit, Section 4.7.2 Rec 8)."
